    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Third doses of mRNA COVID-19 vaccines induced a significant increase in neutralizing potency and breadth in na\u00efve individuals comparable with convalescents who restored levels after the first two doses. These results suggest a limit to elicit neutralization in the number of stimuli by infection or vaccination with ancestral SARS-CoV-2 sequences</jats:p>",
